现金流量附表概述&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>现金流量附表原理解析（四）</title><link>//localhost:1313/post/%E8%B4%A2%E6%8A%80/%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A1/%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E9%99%84%E8%A1%A8%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E5%9B%9B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Aug 2023 11:12:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/post/%E8%B4%A2%E6%8A%80/%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A1/%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E9%99%84%E8%A1%A8%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E5%9B%9B/</guid><description>&lt;p>今天主要整理一下现金流量附表中每一个项目的取数逻辑。&lt;/p>
